com.konakartadmin.app

Class AdminTagConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.konakartadmin.app.AdminTagConstraint

  • public class AdminTagConstraint
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to add one or more tag constraints to a customer search. The constraints in multiple AdminTagConstraint objects are AND'ed together. The array of AdminTagInnerConstraint objects within a single AdminTagConstraint object are OR'ed together.
